{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0611","source_sequence":611,"primary_authority_library":"S02","source_line_start":2677,"source_line_end":2679,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十一·同盘异命论与夫妻对待辨析","parent_section":"二、慧明居士观点讨论之一：化忌之星逢化禄","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"  又，生年禄入大限父母宫，主光明。
