{"clause_group_id":"6","contribution_mode_code":"0","external_source_file_dependency":"NO","line_id":"D","normalized_text":"【宫垣定义】","normalized_text_sha256":"cec6fa327279f2ae2c806e44c7ad7d4bff39f6ace9b98fd896a313d8b5fd6f1d","raw_text":"【宫垣定义】","raw_text_sha256":"cec6fa327279f2ae2c806e44c7ad7d4bff39f6ace9b98fd896a313d8b5fd6f1d","runtime_atom_text_id":"S07-RAT-6","runtime_read_status":"PASS","section_id":"4","source_atom_id":"6"}
{"clause_group_id":"7","contribution_mode_code":"0","external_source_file_dependency":"NO","line_id":"E","normalized_text":"“宫垣”系指命盘十二宫：命宫(身宫)、兄弟宫、夫妻宫、子女宫、财帛宫、疾厄宫、迁移宫、交友宫、官禄宫、田宅宫、福德宫、父母宫。","normalized_text_sha256":"69253788398481082eb9a1b34dbae518db2c5a886cfda4520c0da903611fdc5b","raw_text":"“宫垣”系指命盘十二宫：命宫(身宫)、兄弟宫、夫妻宫、子女宫、财帛宫、疾厄宫、迁移宫、交友宫、事业宫、田宅宫、福德宫、父母宫。","raw_text_sha256":"cc3337183c11b27ffd439e11ff31678bc0aa02785db39f21fe366605591e5ce5","runtime_atom_text_id":"S07-RAT-7","runtime_read_status":"PASS","section_id":"4","source_atom_id":"7"}
