{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0210","line_start":806,"line_end":811,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫分析：
