{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00041","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-003-0002","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":3,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论天地干支所出","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":163,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":2,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"窃以奸诈生，妖怪出。黄帝时有蚩尤神扰乱，当是之时，黄帝甚忧民之苦，遂战蚩尤于涿鹿之野（涿鹿，郡名）。流血百里，不能治之（时帝始制干戈刀剑之器），黄帝于是斋戒筑坛祀天，方丘礼地。天乃降十干（即：甲、乙、丙、丁、戊、己、庚、辛、壬、癸），十二支（即：子、丑、寅、卯、辰、巳、午、未、申、酉、戌、亥）。帝乃将十干圆布象天形；十二支方布象地形。始以干为天，支为地，合光仰职门放之，然后乃能治也（此十干、十二支之所出也）。自后有大挠氏，为后人忧之曰：嗟呼！黄帝乃圣人，尚不能治其恶杀，万一后世见灾被苦，将何奈乎！遂将十干、十二支分配成六十甲子云。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"843500863f10461fbd63af3ca38e2bdeac66888bf54b0cdaecdf1986c6253c1e","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["CONDITION","LIMITATION_OR_CONTRAST","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S11","CROSS_ROUTES":[],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-003","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00040","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00042"}
