{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00179","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-015-0004","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":15,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论天干生旺死绝","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":779,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":4,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"甲亥子丑寅卯辰巳午未申酉戌乙午巳辰卯寅丑子亥戌酉申未丙寅卯辰巳午未申酉戌亥子丑丁酉申未午巳辰卯寅丑子亥戌戊寅卯辰巳午未申酉戌亥子丑己酉申未午巳辰卯寅丑子亥戌庚巳午未申酉戌亥子丑寅卯辰辛子亥戌酉申未午巳辰卯寅丑壬申酉戌亥子丑寅卯辰巳午未癸卯寅丑子亥戌酉申未午巳辰眉批：","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"faa16de0a0d8ac53390b2211d14d6a26a4329826350a9a41ad31a89c3414a26b","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["NEGATION"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S11","CROSS_ROUTES":["S12"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-015","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00178","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00180"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00180","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-015-0005","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":15,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论天干生旺死绝","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":781,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":5,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"长生者，言物在於发生而出，如人受父母精血延怀十月而生也。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"df20b51e89168695c6728e7cdb82e931ff55e3645a1d6ee6f910b38452ce58da","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["CONDITION","QUANTITY"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S11","CROSS_ROUTES":["S12","S16"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-015","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00179","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00181"}

{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00865","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-081-0004","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":81,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论印绶","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":4061,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":4,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"盖印绶畏财，主人括囊。故四柱中及运行官贵反成其福，盖官鬼能生印。只畏其财，而财又能伤我。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"838dd479a73fe6d262f7d05c8f64ea58e0e1e3c7dee7183be3c566563b8ef9f5","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","LIMITATION_OR_CONTRAST","QUANTITY","REFERENCE","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S11","CROSS_ROUTES":[],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-081","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00864","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00866"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00866","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-081-0005","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":81,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论印绶","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":4063,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":5,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"此印绶之妙者，多是受父母之荫，承父母赀财，现成安享之人。若又以两三命相并，当以印绶多者为上。又主一生少病，能饮食。或若财多乘旺，必多淹留。虽喜官鬼而官鬼多或入格，又不可专以印绶言之。假如甲乙日得亥子月生，丙丁日得寅卯月生，戊己日得巳午月生，庚辛日得辰戌丑未月生，壬癸日得申酉月生者是也，其余以类言之。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"6c89808f83012631f75b4eb4d0c077644d183929fea2100a58d195f20399b252","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","LIMITATION_OR_CONTRAST","NECESSARY","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S11","CROSS_ROUTES":["S12","S13","S16"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-081","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00865","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00867"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00867","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-081-0006","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":81,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论印绶","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":4065,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":6,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"最怕行印绶死绝运或运临死绝，复有物以窃之，即入黄泉，不可疑也。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"41409ec376880e133d6352161deee17adde6b9890a663ed488e41e5edf2c6f49","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CONDITION","NEGATION"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S11","CROSS_ROUTES":["S12"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-081","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00866","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S00868"}

{"YHZP_EDITORIAL_RECORD_ID":"YHZP-ED-00031","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":2,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论五行所生之始","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":153,"SOURCE_LAYER":"EDITORIAL_MODERN_NOTE","RAW_TEXT":"文明让人类获得了秩序与智识，又永久失去了什么？","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"fe5404e5fe06bfbd3db30992922e5f0f93dc12fffb7ed5001417c5ea6a2a71b9","ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"ZERO","RUNTIME_RULE_AUTHORITY":"NO","STATUS":"ARCHIVE_AND_SEARCH_ONLY"}
{"YHZP_EDITORIAL_RECORD_ID":"YHZP-ED-00032","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":3,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论天地干支所出","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":172,"SOURCE_LAYER":"EDITORIAL_TRANSLATION","RAW_TEXT":"话说奸邪之气滋生，妖异之事随之而出。黄帝在位时，蚩尤神兴兵作乱，扰乱天下。彼时黄帝忧心百姓之苦，遂率军与蚩尤战于涿鹿之野（涿鹿，郡名）。血流百里，久战难平（此时黄帝才开始制造干戈刀剑等兵器）。黄帝于是斋戒沐浴，筑坛祭天，以方丘之礼祀地。上天因此降下十天干（甲、乙、丙、丁、戊、己、庚、辛、壬、癸）与十二地支（子、丑、寅、卯、辰、巳、午、未、申、酉、戌、亥）。黄帝将十天干排布成圆形，以象天之形；将十二地支排布成方形，以象地之形。以干为天，以支为地，合天地之象而统御万职，从此方能治理天下。此即十干、十二支之来历。此后有大挠氏，忧虑后世之人，叹道：黄帝乃圣人，尚且难以平息祸乱，倘若后世再遭灾厄，又将如何应对？遂将十干与十二支相互配合，推演出六十甲子之循环。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"5542ac59eb8eb1e363263e77f8583935eb383d54266591ee2fdf20bd1c6d3b29","ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"ZERO","RUNTIME_RULE_AUTHORITY":"NO","STATUS":"ARCHIVE_AND_SEARCH_ONLY"}
