{"YHZP_EDITORIAL_RECORD_ID":"YHZP-ED-00329","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":32,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论福星贵人","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":1469,"SOURCE_LAYER":"EDITORIAL_TRANSLATION","RAW_TEXT":"本段以又诀形式，逐一列出十天干对应的\"福星贵人\"所在地支位置。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"14947489235fcdd3325c61b6bf9b5e48dabe2ac00422876aca3598bc62a7604b","ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"ZERO","RUNTIME_RULE_AUTHORITY":"NO","STATUS":"ARCHIVE_AND_SEARCH_ONLY"}
{"YHZP_EDITORIAL_RECORD_ID":"YHZP-ED-00330","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":32,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论福星贵人","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":1471,"SOURCE_LAYER":"EDITORIAL_TRANSLATION","RAW_TEXT":"甲日与丙日出生者，以寅（虎乡）为福星贵人之地，若再见子（鼠穴），力量更强；戊日生人贵人在申（猴），己日生人贵人在未（羊），丁日生人贵人宜落亥（猪）；丙日生人还特别钟爱戌中所藏之气。庚日生人贵人在午（马），辛日生人贵人在巳（蛇），壬日生人贵人在辰（龙），喜逢此位。另外丁日生人亦喜酉 （鸡）；癸日与乙日生人，贵人在丑（牛）与卯（兔），得之则自然昌盛。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"3217f9c14593c66e61163dfd834484bd3217247557a533bf112bc99b5bee0995","ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"ZERO","RUNTIME_RULE_AUTHORITY":"NO","STATUS":"ARCHIVE_AND_SEARCH_ONLY"}
