{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01467","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-160-0005","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":160,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论大运","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7596,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":5,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"出癸入甲，如返汗之人，多主不吉。古语云：伤寒换阳，行运换甲，换过是人，换不过是鬼。且如甲戌接癸亥，此乃干支接木。丑运交寅，辰交巳、未交申、戌交亥，此乃转角接木。东南西北，四方转角谓之接木，格局凶者死，格局善者灾，老人大忌，後生差慢。寅卯辰一气，巳午未一气，申酉戌一气，亥子丑一气，气之相连，皆非接木之说，纵遇接甲，亦无大祸。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"36c2e49ac67b5cb5c5d87b464a319a4097a778b1592044a9121d74bc55481db9","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S11","S12","S13"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-160","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01466","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01468"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01468","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-160-0006","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":160,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论大运","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7598,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":6,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"且如甲乙得寅卯运，名曰劫财、败财，主克父母及克妻，破财争斗之事。行丙丁巳午运名伤官，主克子女，讼事囚系。行庚申辛酉，七杀官乡，主得名，发越太过则灾病恶疾。行壬癸亥子生气印绶运，主吉庆增産。辰戌丑未戊己财运主名利皆通。此乃死法，譬喻须随格局喜忌推之，不可执一，妙在识其通变，拙说如神。干旺宜行衰运，干弱宜旺运，正乃“干弱则求气旺之籍，有余则喜不足之营”。须要通变，更兼孤寡、空亡、勾绞、丧门、吊客、宅墓、病死、官符、白虎诸杀推之，其验如神。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"0db00e6c9f2384e72cb3233c39827d9cee1837dc266ec6c4043ee3cb338e4cd2","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","NECESSARY","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S11","S13","S14","S16"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-160","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01467","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01469"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01469","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-160-0007","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":160,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论大运","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7600,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":7,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"又一法。羊刃、桃花、伏吟、反吟、死绝、衰败者凶运。帝旺、临官、禄马、贵人、生养、冠带、库者吉。如空者，凶空者反吉，吉空者反凶。大运不宜与太岁相克相冲，相冲者凶，更刑冲相克者亦忌。岁冲克运者吉，运克岁者凶，格局不吉者死。岁运相生者吉，禄马贵人合交互者亦吉。宜审细推之，无有不应验者矣。夫运者，人生之传舍。探命之说，尤以三元、四柱、五行、生死、格局致合，以定根基，然後考核运气，协而从之，以定平生之凶吉也。且根基如木，运气如春，春无木而不着，木无春而不荣。赋以根基浅薄者，如蒿莱之微，春风潜发，亦能敷茂，岂能久耶。根基厚壮者，如松柏之实，不为岁寒所变，此所谓先论根基，後言运气者欤。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"e03658d53cd40cb31c5771c56207f395ab7bdf7d985bc5e94f265fa43d1814ec","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","LIMITATION_OR_CONTRAST","NECESSARY","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S11","S12","S13","S14"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-160","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01468","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01470"}

{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01475","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-160-0013","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":160,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论大运","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7612,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":13,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"又曰：丁丑人行丁未运，名曰将凡入圣，以假为真，不以退神论。四柱有丁丑丁未者，不在此限。若戊寅人行丁丑运，虽是退神，却有济化为福。若庚辰生人，或庚辰月行乙酉运，乙酉生人，或乙酉月行庚辰运，名曰鸳鸯两两，主发迹，但重叠者不佳。乙庚人酉年月日时者，大凶。甲申人行丙寅运名曰力停相冲，主破财争竞，屈伸不辨。丙戌人行辛卯运，主钝滞，只宜武人。丙子人行壬寅运，壬入丙家，破财不吉。余仿此推。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"f480eef79ed2b173c2778bc175d863f459d543780d3e1fad1736fdf65ebad0ca","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","LIMITATION_OR_CONTRAST","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":[],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-160","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01474","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01476"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01476","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-160-0014","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":160,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论大运","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7614,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":14,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"又曰：凡命有气象，常取生时干神为气，四柱干神为象，则甲己则有土气，乙庚有金气，丙辛有水气之类为化象，甲乙丙丁为本象，行运至气象得地处吉，不得地处凶。庚辛壬癸乙庚丙辛为金水象，运至申酉丑上得地。庚辛戊己甲乙乙庚为金土象，运至申酉辰上得地。庚辛丙丁乙庚戊癸为金火象，运至巳午戌上得地。庚辛甲乙乙庚丁壬为金木象，运至丑寅卯上得地。甲乙壬癸丁壬丙辛为水木象，运至亥子辰上得地。丙丁甲乙戊癸丁壬为火木象，运至寅卯未上得地。戊己壬癸甲己丙辛为水土象，运至辰上得地。戊己丙丁戊癸甲己为火土象，运至戌上得地。戊己甲乙甲己丁壬为土水象，运至未上得地。戊己庚辛乙庚甲己为金土象，运至丑上得地。看四柱干神得何象，如纯金木水火土，亦为五象，若杂而不入象者不发，发亦不久。如五纯象亦有太过之象，仍详当生月令得地，然後看行运得地不得地而言，不可以遇禄马贵人为得运，遇空亡羊刃劫杀为失运也。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"7199cfc84191e923bfe65b619d5abeb7e6abac48abdc981af5856773d4536b14","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","LIMITATION_OR_CONTRAST","NEGATION","QUANTITY","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S12"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-160","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01475","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01477"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01477","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-160-0015","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":160,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论大运","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7616,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":15,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"又曰：凡行运，看纳音年庚金木水火土是何命人，如土命而行西南方，为西南得朋之庆。木命而行东方，火命而行南方，金命而行西方，水命而行北方，皆为得地。更看所行之运纳音与命相孚同类，最为上吉，财官次之。若泄气或受克重则不吉。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"015b61667b65ff106cc1b5e6a5d7a013520cb352d0989651120ef633557a1337","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","NEGATION","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S11"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-160","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01476","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01478"}

{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01486","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-162-0004","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":162,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论运化气","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7689,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":4,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"至於合而化者，取其岁首月建天干五行所生之五行。如甲己之年正月为丙寅，天干丙火生土，所以甲己合就化土；乙庚之年正月为戊寅，天干戊土生金，所以乙庚合化金；丙辛之年正月为庚寅，天干庚金生水，所以丙辛合化水。余仿此。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"4325cc470990ca5af0a954f278f1a6c5e252061efd7f7d2bf37a8b0846a06306","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["CAUSAL","CONDITION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S13","S14"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-162","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01485","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01487"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01487","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-162-0005","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":162,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论运化气","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7691,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":5,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"甲己化土，中正之合。辰戌丑未全曰稼穑，勾陈得位。乙庚化金，仁义之合，巳酉丑全曰从革。戊癸化火，无情之合，得火局曰炎上。丙辛化水得申子辰水局曰润下。丁壬化木，得亥卯未全曰仁寿。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"0aebd95743f714de46f84577b4373204d8564169bc00910d9f673f7715e1f0db","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["CONDITION","NEGATION"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S13","S14","S16"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-162","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01486","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01488"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01488","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-162-0006","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":162,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论运化气","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7693,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":6,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"天干化合者，秀气。地支合局者，福德。化之真者，名公巨卿。化之假者，孤儿异性。逢龙即化，变作飞龙在天，利见大人。月令生旺，养库临官之地方化。阴阳得合，夫妇匹配，中和之气而化，太过不及皆不能化。有夫从妻化，妻从夫化，正化、偏化，日下自化。转角化，乃未坤申，丑艮寅。经云：东北丧朋，西北得朋。甲日见己字化土，己见甲亦然，乃化之真谓之正化。化之真者名公巨卿，乃富贵之格。化之假者孤儿异姓，或为僧道之类。十干效此推之。但戊癸化火，南木化午，北不化子。午乃少明君火，所以不化。寅申乃少阳火，乃化。经云：化之格局，玄中又玄，妙中又妙，不可俱述。常观天元神趣八法：返、照、鬼、伏、类、属、从、化，仔细推详。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"5d6ff7b09b1c1b8e669523c745288ee69f3fb374b78a53fe83f510fbb2de809f","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","LIMITATION_OR_CONTRAST","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S15","CROSS_ROUTES":["S11","S12","S13","S14","S16"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-162","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01487","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01489"}

