{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01450","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-159-0003","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":159,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论疾病","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7509,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":3,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"夫疾病者，乃精神血气之所主，各有感伤。内曰脏腑，外曰肢体。八字干支五行生克之义，取伤重者而断之。五行干支太旺不及俱病。金主刀刃相伤，水乃溺舟而死，木乃悬梁自缢、虎啖蛇咬，火则夜眠颠倒、蛇伤烧焚，土乃山崩石压、泥陷墙崩。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"48ef35a92b1a4850c6ab3297cb955ddb5ba868f95fcfdc9bf0240c99668adde7","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","NEGATION","QUANTITY","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S16","CROSS_ROUTES":["S11","S12"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-159","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01449","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01451"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01451","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-159-0004","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":159,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论疾病","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7511,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":4,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"且如生命，天干内腑所属，诗曰：甲肝乙胆丙小肠，丁心戊胃己脾乡，庚是大肠辛属肺，壬是膀胱癸肾藏。天干外肢所属：甲头乙项丙肩求，丁心戊胁己属腹，庚系人脐辛为股，壬胫癸足自来求。子疝气，丑肚腹，寅臂肢，卯目手，辰背胸，巳面齿，午心腹，未脾胸，申咳疾，酉肝腩，戌背肺，亥头肝。肝乃肾家苗，肾乃肝之主，肾通於眼，胆藏魂，肝藏魄，肾藏精，心藏神，脾藏气。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"d966b2c5457ab815f1f3388c70bfd9ce7291f2df1c0d6e90ab2c5e6ff80d6e09","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["CONDITION","NEGATION","SEQUENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S16","CROSS_ROUTES":[],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-159","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01450","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01452"}
{"YHZP_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01452","SOURCE_ROOT_ATOM_ID":"YHZP-ROOT-159-0005","SOURCE_FAMILY_ID":"YHZP-USER-CLEANED-ROOT-03","CHAPTER_NO":159,"CHAPTER_TITLE":"论疾病","SOURCE_PHYSICAL_LINE_NO":7513,"SOURCE_LINE_SEQ_IN_CHAPTER":5,"SOURCE_LAYER":"CLASSICAL_ORIGINAL","RAW_TEXT":"木命见庚辛申酉多者，肝胆病。内则惊精、虚怯痨疾、呕血、头晕目眩、痰喘、头风脚气、左瘫右痪、又眼歪斜、风症。筋⾻疼痛。外则皮肤乾燥、眼目之疾、发须疏少、颠朴手足损伤之患。女则堕胎、血气不调(堕胎，指孕妇不足月生産，又名小産、早産。血气不调，中医以气为血之帅，血为气之母，二者相互依存，如果不相协和，则可致病，而气血不调就是其病机。在这里指的是因气血不调所致的月经疾病)。小儿急慢惊风，夜啼咳嗽。经云：筋⾻疼痛，盖因木被金伤。","RAW_TEXT_SHA256":"0db41fae7f27aa0b268f12287d71962c253bf2b5f493100f87f1400044bca19e","LOGICAL_OPERATOR_HINTS":["ALTERNATIVE_OR_PARALLEL","CAUSAL","COMPARISON_OR_DEGREE","CONDITION","NECESSARY","NEGATION","QUANTITY","REFERENCE"],"PRIMARY_AUTHORITY_LIBRARY":"S16","CROSS_ROUTES":["S12"],"CURRENT_ASTROLOGICAL_CONTRIBUTION":"FUTURE_CONDITIONAL_ONLY","CURRENT_CASE_EVIDENCE_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_EVENT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_ENDPOINT_PERMISSION":"NO","DIRECT_SCORE_PERMISSION":"NO","STATUS":"ACTIVE_SOURCE","PARENT_CHAPTER_ID":"YHZP-CH-159","PREV_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01451","NEXT_SEGMENT_ID":"YHZP-USR-S01453"}

